title: The Cars - Complete Greatest Hits (2002) [FLAC]
description:
Complete Greatest Hits is a compilation album by the New Wave band The Cars, released in 2002.

It has everything the casual fan might want, including the perfect radio singles "Just What I Needed," "My Best Friend's Girl," "You're All I've Got Tonight," and "Shake It Up." More serious fans might want to go deeper, but the Cars were essentially a singles band, and the group's peak material is here.

Enjoy
